    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require schools allow students to wear shorts and tracksuits.",
        "additional_details": "As from experience the temperature has severely impacted my education as it makes it harder to fully concentrate. The temperature does not only impact my learning, it also impacts other pupils' learning. I also want to make students reach their maximum potential and for them to be able to learn without anything getting in their way.",
        "background": "I want the government to require schools to allow students to wear shorts in extreme hot weathers and tracksuits in cold weather.",
